{"tid":962030,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有病唔睇醫生唔食藥玩邊科","createTime":"2018-12-30T14:28:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-30T16:31:20.000Z","uid":182793,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"56f9b2a07f8bf1aaf601579a424ee9a6a99b6dcd","tid":962030,"uid":182793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T14:28:35.000Z","msg":"有個女性朋友有 感冒又暈又嘔都仲可以死都唔肯食西藥 同埋亦都唔肯睇醫生 話好唔鍾意啲藥苦。 <br />\n<br />\n係咪有啲好草根階層的屋企習慣係咁？？？ <br />\n<br />\n話說呢個係第三都係住公屋的朋友係gum， 屋企環境較為惡劣/ 懶散 會有咁嘅習慣。 <br />\n<br />\n非富戶， 另外識D公屋富戶或者家庭 整體 較為上進 嗰啲 或 私樓 的  朋友係冇呢啲習慣。。。<br />\n<br />\n利伸，自己 老豆都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebe30ddcedeb3709f933d7883df7f1318b829b44","tid":962030,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T14:40:29.000Z","msg":"懶係慳錢咁<br />\n<br />\n但係買垃圾果陣又唔會諗慳錢"},{"pid":"759b6049d3128cd90b9d938420050b4e7f356bae","tid":962030,"uid":150076,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T14:44:46.000Z","msg":"西藥唔係咁好喎講真"},{"pid":"bdbac42d0f99a6c5aa742fc2720459fa095283bf","tid":962030,"uid":150076,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T14:46:35.000Z","msg":"建議樓主睇下啲藥廠紀錄片"},{"pid":"30e5d025ba89d5785122b44128f4b8ef088c2dec","tid":962030,"uid":205844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebe30ddcedeb3709f933d7883df7f1318b829b44","tid":962030,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T14:40:29.000Z","msg":"懶係慳錢咁<br />\n<br />\n但係買垃圾果陣又唔會諗慳錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T14:49:56.000Z","msg":"唔係，佢地多數會話:靠西藥下次d菌仲惡，緊係靠抵抗力去醫返啦/過幾日冇事啦，小小感冒驚乜呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f3dc230779f84dd1a48afabb09133be819dbd90","tid":962030,"uid":205844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ebe30ddcedeb3709f933d7883df7f1318b829b44","tid":962030,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T14:40:29.000Z","msg":"懶係慳錢咁<br />\n<br />\n但係買垃圾